{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"赞歌献给红太阳","authors":["金才"],"dates":[{"year":1968,"month":10,"day":1}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"赞歌献给红太阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蒙古族　金才"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站在莽莽的兴安岭上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翻身牧民放声歌唱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一曲曲赞歌飞向北京城，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"献给我们心中的红太阳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席啊！红太阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灿烂的光辉把内蒙古草原照亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东思想的伟大真理，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把牧民的头脑武装。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"文化大革命烈火旺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"科尔沁草原翻红浪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"各族人民紧跟毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敢教山河换新装。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听，从兴安岭北麓到贺兰山下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个最强烈的声音在回响："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千万名歌手齐声唱啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敬祝毛主席万寿无疆！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}